            f"- v322 재사용: rank {V322_STATS.get('rank_source_reuse',0)} / scan {V322_STATS.get('scan_health_reuse',0)} / 느림감지 rank {V322_STATS.get('rank_source_slow',0)} scan {V322_STATS.get('scan_health_slow',0)}",
            "",
